                    <span class="block w-6 h-px bg-[#0145F2]"></span>
                    <span>Free playbook · Zeffron</span>
                </div>

                <h1 class="hero-headline text-white mb-6"
                    style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.5vw, 4.75rem); letter-spacing: -0.035em; line-height: 1; font-weight: 600;">
                    <span class="hero-line-mask"><span class="hero-line-inner" style="--d: 0.25s;">You have the idea.</span></span>
                    <span class="hero-line-mask"><span class="hero-line-inner" style="--d: 0.37s;">This turns it into</span></span>
                    <span class="hero-line-mask"><span class="hero-line-inner" style="--d: 0.49s;">a product.</span></span>
                </h1>

                <p class="hero-fade text-[#A8A8A8] text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mb-8" style="--fd: 0.85s;">
                    <span class="text-white">50+ AI prompts</span> that take you from messy idea to MVP scope, user stories, and pitch deck — in 30 minutes. The exact framework Zeffron uses to scope every sprint.
                </p>

                <ul class="hero-fade space-y-3 mb-10 max-w-md" style="--fd: 1s;">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#E5E5E5]">
                        <i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#0145F2] shrink-0"></i>
                        Five stages · idea → pitch
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#E5E5E5]">
                        <i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#0145F2] shrink-0"></i>
                        Built for non-technical founders
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#E5E5E5]">
                        <i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#0145F2] shrink-0"></i>
                        MVP readiness quiz included
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <div class="hero-fade flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 sm:items-center mb-6" style="--fd: 1.15s;">
                    <a href="#playbook-form" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
